<div class="title">Watch Your Dosages</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Yancy&Exact=1">Yancy</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Yancy. "Watch Your Dosages: An Experience with AMT (exp13772)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 15, 2002. erowid.org/exp/13772</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

